desc: RubyCee is an online shop offering Bohemian Western style handbags, totes, jewelry and t-shirts. I created RubyCee for the love of fashion accessories and Tees! The name RubyCee came from my Grandmother, whose name is Ruby Christine, and was called Ruby C. She loved fashion and was a classy dresser her entire life.
